815
01:08:49,640 --> 01:08:51,233
but on this I can’t follow you.

816
01:08:52,280 --> 01:08:55,272
Sofia has to pay for what she did,
and she is paying,

817
01:08:55,480 --> 01:08:57,198
and she’ll pay for the rest of her life.

818
01:08:57,440 --> 01:08:59,716
Do you think she’ll ever
shake off what she did?

819
01:08:59,800 --> 01:09:01,518
What she did, she did to me!

820
01:09:03,080 --> 01:09:05,071
You can’t understand, you don’t have children.

821
01:09:06,280 --> 01:09:07,270
You’re right.

822
01:09:07,840 --> 01:09:09,399
I don’t understand. I don’t have any.

823
01:09:10,760 --> 01:09:13,400
But I won’t let them take her child away.
I won’t do that.

824
01:09:14,360 --> 01:09:15,953
I’ll request custody for you,

825
01:09:16,640 --> 01:09:18,199
but she has to stay close to him,

826
01:09:19,520 --> 01:09:21,238
otherwise I’ll step down from the case.

827
01:09:21,920 --> 01:09:25,311
Come to my office tomorrow morning.
We’ll see what can be done.

828
01:09:48,480 --> 01:09:51,393
Here, it’s perfect. Beautiful.

829
01:09:51,480 --> 01:09:55,030
With this hairstyle I’ll get you
a full acquittal.

830
01:09:56,760 --> 01:09:58,751
Oh, tell that to the judge.

831
01:09:58,840 --> 01:10:02,754
Sharon Catalucci, hairdresser.
Maybe he’ll reduce my sentence.

832
01:10:03,560 --> 01:10:09,670
Sofia, I’ve read the report
your counselor sent me.

833
01:10:09,760 --> 01:10:11,239
Now it’s your turn.

834
01:10:12,160 --> 01:10:15,710
Are you aware that what you’re asking
is extremely important?

835
01:10:17,440 --> 01:10:18,589
Yes, of course.

836
01:10:19,120 --> 01:10:22,431
[judge] I don’t need to explain
the seriousness of what you did.

837
01:10:23,160 --> 01:10:28,872
What do you want to tell me to convince me
that the people here with you—

838
01:10:29,000 --> 01:10:32,959
the social worker, the lawyer—
are right in saying

839
01:10:33,040 --> 01:10:36,635
that you deserve to move
from prison to a community?

840
01:10:41,000 --> 01:10:41,990
I don’t know.

841
01:10:44,600 --> 01:10:48,673
Even though it’s what I want most,
I can’t go back,

842
01:10:49,400 --> 01:10:50,390
and…

843
01:10:50,800 --> 01:10:53,440
I can’t even apologize to anyone,

844
01:10:53,520 --> 01:10:56,273
because how do you apologize
for what I did?

845
01:10:58,800 --> 01:11:01,076
I’ve had a lot of time to think.

846
01:11:01,400 --> 01:11:03,596
I’ve never thought this much in my life.

847
01:11:05,320 --> 01:11:07,231
Prison changed me.

848
01:11:08,000 --> 01:11:10,719
Anna, my counselor,
changed me, and…

849
01:11:12,200 --> 01:11:15,830
this child
changed me more than anything.

850
01:11:18,480 --> 01:11:20,869
I’d like you to trust me

851
01:11:21,400 --> 01:11:25,155
and allow me to raise him
in a home, not in a cell.

852
01:11:26,280 --> 01:11:29,511
That’s what I want: for him to be okay.

853
01:11:29,600 --> 01:11:33,559
If that’s not possible, then maybe…

854
01:11:34,960 --> 01:11:36,997
maybe my father should take care of him.

855
01:11:37,640 --> 01:11:38,755
That’s all.

856
01:11:43,320 --> 01:11:44,310
All right, Sofia.

857
01:11:45,360 --> 01:11:48,273
Please wait, we’ll retire
to deliberate.

859
01:11:56,440 --> 01:11:59,034
“The court, pursuant to Article 299,

860
01:11:59,120 --> 01:12:03,876
replaces pretrial detention
with placement in a community.

861
01:12:04,520 --> 01:12:08,514
Entrusts Sofia Battisti to the social services
of the Ministry of Justice,

862
01:12:08,600 --> 01:12:11,114
which shall identify a suitable community.

863
01:12:11,280 --> 01:12:15,797
Authorizes transfer to the facility
under escort.”

864
01:12:19,440 --> 01:12:21,397
Sofia, get ready to leave.

865
01:12:21,480 --> 01:12:24,916
Stop by Intake to collect
your personal belongings. Congratulations.

866
01:12:27,960 --> 01:12:33,034
You’re getting out! I’m so happy.
Drina, come here! Sofia’s leaving today.

867
01:12:33,120 --> 01:12:35,157
- She’s leaving!
- My love.

868
01:12:35,280 --> 01:12:36,634
- You’re leaving?

869
01:12:36,840 --> 01:12:38,194
Good for you!

871
01:12:46,600 --> 01:12:50,230
How wonderful! Hi, little one.

872
01:12:51,720 --> 01:12:53,074
I’m happy.

873
01:12:58,720 --> 01:13:01,712
There are girls here with serious problems.

874
01:13:01,800 --> 01:13:04,076
Some are in therapy,
some taken away from their families.

875
01:13:04,160 --> 01:13:06,037
- Are we all together?
- Yes, of course,

876
01:13:06,120 --> 01:13:09,795
but you’re under pretrial supervision.
You’ll have different rules and schedules.

877
01:13:09,880 --> 01:13:12,599
You’ll be able to go back to school,
attend classes.

878
01:13:12,920 --> 01:13:16,754
And soon you’ll be able
to go out sometimes with your father.

879
01:13:17,080 --> 01:13:19,117
This is a huge opportunity.

880
01:13:19,480 --> 01:13:22,120
If you’re granted probation
and you don’t mess up,

881
01:13:23,000 --> 01:13:25,753
in three years you’ll be free
with a clean criminal record.

882
01:13:26,200 --> 01:13:29,750
But if…
If I mess up, do I go back to prison?

883
01:13:29,880 --> 01:13:31,279
Why would you mess up?

884
01:13:31,760 --> 01:13:33,398
We believe in you.

885
01:13:33,800 --> 01:13:36,235
The judge also seemed very confident.

886
01:13:36,360 --> 01:13:38,112
Come on, everything will be fine.

887
01:13:38,640 --> 01:13:40,358
Yes, but you won’t be there.

888
01:13:40,720 --> 01:13:42,757
There’s someone better than me
at the community.

889
01:13:43,160 --> 01:13:44,833
Hey, I’m not abandoning you.

890
01:13:47,000 --> 01:13:49,833
Sofia, you have to go. Do you want to stay here?

892
01:13:55,960 --> 01:13:58,429
Uh…

893
01:14:34,520 --> 01:14:38,036
[woman] Soon you’ll start the project.
Everyone liked it.

894
01:14:38,120 --> 01:14:42,034
Bringing horses together with troubled kids
is a great idea.

895
01:14:42,160 --> 01:14:46,233
You’ll need to follow it closely,
behave well, commit to it fully.

896
01:14:46,320 --> 01:14:49,517
I want them to say that no one like you
has ever been there.

897
01:14:57,400 --> 01:14:58,834
Remember…

898
01:14:59,440 --> 01:15:00,794
Hold the reins.

899
01:15:01,640 --> 01:15:03,517
Good, with both hands.

900
01:15:03,960 --> 01:15:06,429
- You’ve gotten really good.
- Thank you, Sofia.

901
01:15:06,520 --> 01:15:07,510
Go on, go on.

902
01:15:09,320 --> 01:15:10,833
Let’s do another lap. Want to?

903
01:15:11,000 --> 01:15:12,399
- Okay.

904
01:15:24,960 --> 01:15:26,553
- Can I touch her?
- Yes.

905
01:15:26,640 --> 01:15:28,790
- Does it bother you?
- Go on, go ahead!

906
01:15:30,120 --> 01:15:31,838
She’s grown so much!

907
01:15:32,240 --> 01:15:33,594
How much longer?

908
01:15:34,040 --> 01:15:35,758
Not much, about a month.

909
01:15:35,880 --> 01:15:39,555
- Will you keep coming here?
- Of course, I’ll bring him too.

910
01:15:40,600 --> 01:15:41,749
Maria, come here!

911
01:15:42,520 --> 01:15:44,989
I have to go, I have to go!
See you Wednesday.

912
01:15:45,280 --> 01:15:47,157
I have to go, I have to go!

913
01:15:52,280 --> 01:15:53,270
Bye!

914
01:15:55,160 --> 01:15:59,313
- Wait, go.
- Go on, there—oh!

917
01:16:24,720 --> 01:16:28,429
[woman] You took the girl away from her family
to keep her here,

918
01:16:28,520 --> 01:16:32,832
with crazies on medication,
ex-prostitutes, and a murderer!

919
01:16:33,440 --> 01:16:36,956
- What’s going on, Carolina?
- My mother is crazy.

920
01:16:37,080 --> 01:16:40,596
- You’re brainwashing her!
- Calm down, ma’am.

921
01:16:40,720 --> 01:16:43,599
- I will not calm down!
- Request a revocation of the measure.

922
01:16:43,720 --> 01:16:45,518
- I’ll report you!
- We were calm

923
01:16:45,600 --> 01:16:47,511
- and I mentioned you.
- I’m taking her home!

924
01:16:47,600 --> 01:16:51,150
- Do as you wish.
- I’m going to file a complaint…

925
01:16:51,240 --> 01:16:53,880
- Watch your tone.
- …because you’re crazy and incompetent!

926
01:16:53,960 --> 01:16:56,634
- You don’t know who I am.
- I don’t care.

927
01:16:56,720 --> 01:16:58,518
- I’ll report you!
- Learn to listen.

928
01:16:58,600 --> 01:17:02,195
Do whatever you want,
but let us do our work.

929
01:17:02,280 --> 01:17:03,998
Goodbye, ma’am. Excuse me.

930
01:17:04,360 --> 01:17:08,149
- Don’t worry, nothing happened.
- They should give *her* the medication.

931
01:17:08,480 --> 01:17:11,438
Come on. Marta, you come too, let’s go.

932
01:17:11,720 --> 01:17:13,757
- I’m going, see you later.
- Yes.

934
01:18:07,040 --> 01:18:08,758
Here you go, hot and fresh.

935
01:18:25,600 --> 01:18:27,352
What’s wrong with her? Why isn’t she eating?

936
01:18:28,360 --> 01:18:30,112
She’s… she’s upset.

937
01:18:30,800 --> 01:18:33,235
She had a breakdown
and they put her back on medication.

938
01:18:33,760 --> 01:18:37,276
Today she went after Livia.
She scratched her all over.

939
01:18:38,000 --> 01:18:40,913
- She won’t last long.
- How dare you?

940
01:18:41,040 --> 01:18:42,314
- Mind your own business!
- Enough!

941
01:18:42,400 --> 01:18:44,755
- Look at the state you’re in.
- What the fuck do you want?!

942
01:18:44,840 --> 01:18:46,592
I’m sick of your shit!

944
01:18:48,080 --> 01:18:49,957
Enough… enough!

945
01:18:50,360 --> 01:18:51,634
Girls, what’s going on?

946
01:18:52,400 --> 01:18:54,835
You pissed her off, you idiot!

947
01:18:54,920 --> 01:18:57,560
- What’s going on here?
- You’re a piece of shit!

948
01:18:57,640 --> 01:18:58,914
- Shut up!
- Girls!

949
01:18:59,000 --> 01:19:00,354
- What’s going on?
- Nothing.

950
01:19:00,440 --> 01:19:04,399
- Nothing’s going on.
- What’s going on is that she never shuts up.

951
01:19:04,480 --> 01:19:07,074
Come on, try to sort it out.
Sofia, are you ready?

952
01:19:07,200 --> 01:19:10,079
- Hurry up, you’ve got the ultrasound.
- Will you come with me?

953
01:19:10,160 --> 01:19:12,037
No, they gave permission to your dad.

954
01:19:12,200 --> 01:19:13,679
He’s taking you today.

955
01:19:13,920 --> 01:19:16,753
Girls, relax. See you later.

957
01:19:17,960 --> 01:19:18,950
Thank you.

958
01:19:27,680 --> 01:19:28,670
Dad.

959
01:19:31,080 --> 01:19:34,152
Sweetheart… good afternoon.

960
01:19:34,320 --> 01:19:35,310
Thanks.

961
01:19:40,120 --> 01:19:41,110
Hi.

962
01:19:43,080 --> 01:19:44,195
How are you?

963
01:19:45,320 --> 01:19:46,833
Fine. Fine…

964
01:19:48,960 --> 01:19:53,670
- How is it there? Are you settling in?
- Fine, fine, yes.

965
01:19:56,880 --> 01:19:58,154
- Let’s go.

966
01:20:33,680 --> 01:20:35,671
[doctor] You’re going to feel a bit of cold now.

967
01:20:40,040 --> 01:20:41,997
Now I’ll poke him a little.

968
01:20:43,680 --> 01:20:45,591
He’s moving a lot.

969
01:20:47,200 --> 01:20:48,190
There we go.

970
01:20:51,640 --> 01:20:53,790
So, did they tell you the sex?

971
01:20:53,920 --> 01:20:56,116
No. Can you already tell?

972
01:20:56,200 --> 01:20:59,318
- Of course, she’ll be born in a month.
- What is it?

973
01:21:00,320 --> 01:21:02,516
It’s a… it’s a beautiful baby girl.

974
01:21:03,960 --> 01:21:04,950
[Sofia] Oh my God…

975
01:21:05,640 --> 01:21:08,280
- Do you know when she’s due?
  
976
01:21:09,040 --> 01:21:14,114
Based on the last menstrual cycle,
around October 20th or 22nd.

977
01:21:14,320 --> 01:21:15,640
- Okay.
- [Pietro] Like Chiara.

978
01:21:16,200 --> 01:21:18,760
- Like who?
- No… no, nothing.

979
01:21:21,520 --> 01:21:23,272
What’s wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

980
01:21:23,640 --> 01:21:24,914
No, just a little…

981
01:21:25,840 --> 01:21:27,399
A little dizzy.

982
01:21:27,880 --> 01:21:29,234
I’ll wait outside.

983
01:21:48,320 --> 01:21:49,640
Are you worried?

984
01:21:50,560 --> 01:21:51,550
No.

985
01:21:53,000 --> 01:21:57,278
You don’t have to be scared, okay?
Babies are simple when they’re little.

986
01:21:58,200 --> 01:22:00,635
You feed them, bathe them,

987
01:22:00,720 --> 01:22:03,678
sing them a song,
and they’re happy.

988
01:22:04,440 --> 01:22:06,078
I used to do that with you too.

989
01:22:08,640 --> 01:22:10,631
You’ll see, you’ll be a good mother.

990
01:22:14,080 --> 01:22:15,957
- Dad.
- Yes?

991
01:22:19,560 --> 01:22:21,198
Earlier you mentioned Chiara.

992
01:22:22,680 --> 01:22:23,670
No.

993
01:22:24,520 --> 01:22:25,510
No.

994
01:22:30,880 --> 01:22:32,598
What time do you have to be back at the facility?

995
01:22:33,920 --> 01:22:34,910
Soon.

997
01:22:47,360 --> 01:22:49,078
[TV] Damn it.

998
01:22:51,200 --> 01:22:53,953
I think I’ll never have one.

999
01:22:57,320 --> 01:22:58,754
- Are you sad?
- No.

1000
01:22:58,880 --> 01:23:00,279
Marta? Come on.

1001
01:23:00,480 --> 01:23:02,949
Go help Livia unload the groceries.

1002
01:23:03,040 --> 01:23:04,360
She can’t do it alone.

1003
01:23:04,800 --> 01:23:06,199
I love you very much.

1004
01:23:06,640 --> 01:23:09,473
[Marta] Girls, come help me with the groceries?

1005
01:23:09,560 --> 01:23:11,039
Come on, Sofia’s tired.

1006
01:23:13,120 --> 01:23:15,714
- [man] Heating?
- It’s independent.

1007
01:23:15,920 --> 01:23:18,833
Here’s the control unit,
but it can also be operated remotely.

1008
01:23:19,720 --> 01:23:23,156
- Condo fees?
- Average, about 120 euros.

1009
01:23:23,240 --> 01:23:27,279
Air conditioning in every room,
and here we have this beauty.

1010
01:23:27,560 --> 01:23:28,550
There you go.

1011
01:23:34,840 --> 01:23:37,992
Southeast exposure, swimming pool, daycare,

1012
01:23:38,080 --> 01:23:40,515
and behind us is one
of the biggest parks in Rome.

1013
01:23:40,600 --> 01:23:42,034
Perfect for a child.

1014
01:23:51,400 --> 01:23:55,234
We should make a substitution next time,
otherwise they never win.

1015
01:23:55,320 --> 01:23:57,550
Do you feel like grabbing something
at the bar with Stefano?

1016
01:23:57,640 --> 01:23:58,630
Yes!

1017
01:24:01,800 --> 01:24:03,518
I don’t want to ask for custody anymore.

1018
01:24:05,080 --> 01:24:08,118
- What do you mean?
- She has to stay with Sofia.

1019
01:24:13,160 --> 01:24:15,151
What can I say, I’m happy.

1020
01:24:15,640 --> 01:24:16,960
It’s the best thing.

1021
01:24:18,440 --> 01:24:20,670
The other day I saw an apartment and…

1022
01:24:22,400 --> 01:24:24,357
I thought it would be perfect.

1023
01:24:25,760 --> 01:24:27,876
They could live there with me as soon as…

1024
01:24:28,560 --> 01:24:30,517
As soon as she’s granted probation.

1025
01:24:30,840 --> 01:24:33,878
So I can go ahead with the request? Are you sure?

1026
01:24:37,080 --> 01:24:38,878
I’m not sure of anything anymore,

1027
01:24:39,800 --> 01:24:41,234
but she’s my daughter and…

1028
01:24:42,480 --> 01:24:43,879
she’s expecting a baby.

1029
01:24:45,680 --> 01:24:47,034
What else can I do?

1031
01:25:00,880 --> 01:25:03,190
Livia! Livia!

1032
01:25:03,280 --> 01:25:04,509
- What’s happening?
- Livia…

1033
01:25:04,600 --> 01:25:08,355
- Yes, tell me.
- Sofia is having nightmares again!

1034
01:25:08,480 --> 01:25:13,350
- I can’t do it! Please, come!
- Let’s go. Stay calm.

1035
01:25:16,520 --> 01:25:18,875
- Help!
- Why are you screaming?

1036
01:25:18,960 --> 01:25:22,874
Stop it! I want to sleep.

1037
01:25:23,040 --> 01:25:27,113
- Stop it!
- No!

1039
01:25:37,560 --> 01:25:39,710
Help! I can’t do it…

1040
01:25:39,800 --> 01:25:42,155
- I can’t do it.
- Everything’s fine.

1041
01:25:42,240 --> 01:25:43,435
Do what we told you.

1043
01:25:46,160 --> 01:25:47,878
Oh God, she’s slipping… she’s slipping!

1044
01:25:47,960 --> 01:25:49,633
I can see the head. Do you want to feel it?

1045
01:25:49,760 --> 01:25:50,989
It burns!

1046
01:25:51,600 --> 01:25:55,116
Come on, now you have to push, Sofi’.
Come on, take a deep breath.

1047
01:25:55,200 --> 01:25:58,158
- Come on, just a little more. Push, Sofia.
- It burns!

1048
01:25:58,240 --> 01:26:00,038
There she is. Push!

1049
01:26:00,800 --> 01:26:02,632
There she is! There she is!

1051
01:26:07,760 --> 01:26:08,830
Oh God…

1052
01:26:10,320 --> 01:26:11,469
There she is!

1053
01:26:13,720 --> 01:26:14,710
Oh God…

1054
01:26:16,720 --> 01:26:19,553
Push again,
you need to expel the placenta.

1056
01:26:21,040 --> 01:26:22,360
Good job, Sofia.

1060
01:26:46,160 --> 01:26:49,198
Congratulations, she really is a beautiful baby,

1061
01:26:49,600 --> 01:26:51,193
truly beautiful.

1062
01:26:51,800 --> 01:26:53,029
Thank you.

1063
01:26:57,680 --> 01:26:59,000
My baby girl.

1064
01:27:17,600 --> 01:27:19,273
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

1065
01:27:19,360 --> 01:27:23,194
- I’m Sofia Battisti’s father…
- Ah, Sofia, yes.

1066
01:27:23,400 --> 01:27:26,950
She’s being discharged.
Do I need to sign anything since she’s a minor?

1067
01:27:27,040 --> 01:27:28,917
No, there’s no need, don’t worry.

1068
01:27:29,120 --> 01:27:31,714
And in any case, Sofia has chosen
to stay another 24 hours.

1069
01:27:31,800 --> 01:27:33,757
- We informed the community.
- Oh.

1070
01:27:34,520 --> 01:27:36,158
- Is there a problem?
- No.

1071
01:27:36,240 --> 01:27:38,356
The younger ones often do it to learn.

1072
01:27:38,480 --> 01:27:41,871
We show them how to change her,
how to feed her, things like that.

1073
01:27:41,960 --> 01:27:45,078
- Ah, okay. Can I see her?
- Of course. You know where she is?

1074
01:27:45,160 --> 01:27:46,958
- Yes, thank you.
- Goodbye.

1075
01:27:47,080 --> 01:27:48,070
Goodbye.

1076
01:27:50,840 --> 01:27:55,437
Yeah, I understand.
Don’t worry, it’s nothing.

1078
01:27:58,360 --> 01:27:59,350
Hi.

1079
01:28:01,280 --> 01:28:03,556
- Hi.
- How are you?

1080
01:28:05,920 --> 01:28:06,910
Fine.

1081
01:28:10,120 --> 01:28:11,349
I brought these for you.

1082
01:28:14,120 --> 01:28:15,190
I’ll leave them here.

1083
01:28:20,080 --> 01:28:21,718
The nurse told me that…

1084
01:28:22,160 --> 01:28:24,595
That you want to stay
one more day in the hospital.

1086
01:28:27,680 --> 01:28:30,399
Everything okay? I can help you
with the baby if…

1087
01:28:34,080 --> 01:28:35,070
Where
is she?

1088
01:28:35,800 --> 01:28:37,632
She’s in the nursery.

1089
01:28:39,280 --> 01:28:41,715
- I’ll go get her.
- No.

1090
01:28:43,920 --> 01:28:46,116
I need to take care of my baby myself.

1091
01:28:48,800 --> 01:28:50,996
Of course… of course, obviously.

1092
01:28:51,560 --> 01:28:52,834
I just wanted to…

1093
01:28:56,840 --> 01:28:57,830
Listen…

1094
01:28:59,480 --> 01:29:01,312
It was supposed to be a surprise, but…

1095
01:29:07,920 --> 01:29:12,118
I got an apartment
near a nice park, for the three of us.

1096
01:29:13,360 --> 01:29:15,510
So you can keep studying and…

1097
01:29:16,120 --> 01:29:18,839
maybe go out with your friends.

1098
01:29:18,920 --> 01:29:20,638
- I’ll take care of the baby.
- No.

1099
01:29:26,640 --> 01:29:29,234
Chiara’s nausea
wasn’t the flu, was it?

1100
01:29:31,960 --> 01:29:34,190
That day at the gynecologist…


1101
01:29:35,800 --> 01:29:36,790
What?

1102
01:29:41,120 --> 01:29:42,952
Was Chiara expecting a baby?

1103
01:29:55,960 --> 01:29:56,950
Yes.

1104
01:30:01,400 --> 01:30:04,756
You’ll always think about it,
because I did something that…

1105
01:30:05,280 --> 01:30:10,878
I did something only a monster would do,
and if I stayed with you, I’d always be one.

1106
01:30:11,000 --> 01:30:12,035
<i>- No.</i>

1107
01:30:12,120 --> 01:30:14,236
- That’s not true. That’s not true.
- Yes.

1108
01:30:14,440 --> 01:30:18,115
Before, yes, before it was like that.
You’re right, but…

1109
01:30:18,200 --> 01:30:19,679
Everything has changed.

1110
01:30:20,000 --> 01:30:22,071
I’d do anything
for our baby girl.

1111
01:30:22,160 --> 01:30:23,309
She’s not ours, she’s mine.

1112
01:30:23,720 --> 01:30:26,553
Of course. Yes, she’s your daughter.

1113
01:30:33,720 --> 01:30:35,154
What should I do?

1114
01:30:37,200 --> 01:30:38,998
Tell me and I’ll… I’ll do it.

1115
01:30:45,720 --> 01:30:47,313
You have to leave, Dad.

1116
01:30:48,080 --> 01:30:49,195
Please.

1117
01:30:50,320 --> 01:30:53,312
She and I will grow up on our own and…

1118
01:30:54,320 --> 01:30:57,073
I have to do it this way, please.

1119
01:31:19,400 --> 01:31:20,390
Dad…

1120
01:31:23,400 --> 01:31:25,357
I need to ask you one more thing.

1121
01:31:27,800 --> 01:31:28,790
Tell me.

1122
01:31:30,400 --> 01:31:32,710
[Statini] Of course, I’ll speak to the head physician
and let you know.

1123
01:31:32,800 --> 01:31:34,154
- All right.
- Goodbye.

1125
01:31:44,560 --> 01:31:48,952
Here comes Grandpa!
I’ve got some good news for you.

1126
01:31:49,280 --> 01:31:51,954
Within a year the judge might
approve probation,

1127
01:31:52,040 --> 01:31:53,872
so Sofia and the baby
could come live with you.

1128
01:31:53,960 --> 01:31:55,598
No, sorry, I can’t…

1129
01:31:56,200 --> 01:31:57,634
I’ve changed my mind.

1130
01:31:59,640 --> 01:32:03,713
- I don’t understand.
- I can’t do it, I can’t…

1131
01:32:04,560 --> 01:32:09,839
I really can’t. I don’t want
to take care of Sofia and the baby.

1132
01:32:10,160 --> 01:32:14,791
- So?
- I talked to her and she understood, so…

1133
01:32:15,840 --> 01:32:19,117
I think it’s the best thing.
She’ll spend the next few years in the community,

1134
01:32:19,440 --> 01:32:21,829
- All right.
- With her daughter.

1135
01:32:24,360 --> 01:32:26,590
- With Rosa.
- Her name is Rosa.

1136
01:32:27,320 --> 01:32:28,310
Yes.

1137
01:32:29,280 --> 01:32:31,749
- It’s a beautiful name.
- Yes.

1138
01:32:32,920 --> 01:32:34,399
Sorry, I have to go.

1140
01:33:54,560 --> 01:33:58,599
[Pietro] After every disaster,
life presents itself again and starts over,

1141
01:33:59,840 --> 01:34:02,354
and that’s what you’re looking for, my daughter.

1142
01:34:02,920 --> 01:34:06,675
Every wound heals,
mine will heal too,

1143
01:34:07,480 --> 01:34:10,472
and if a day comes
when you need something,

1144
01:34:10,680 --> 01:34:14,958
or you want to fall asleep
under the gaze of someone who loves you,

1145
01:34:15,640 --> 01:34:18,359
know that I will never stop waiting for you.

1146
01:34:19,080 --> 01:34:22,232
A child must stop being a child one day,

1147
01:34:22,680 --> 01:34:25,752
but a parent can never stop
being a parent.

1148
01:34:26,840 --> 01:34:28,513
Whatever happens.

